column5: Thats it. Im done.  Time to dust off the long rod,  See ya out there on the toon soon.
I'll put a "Reserved" sign on your spot on the river!
Yup. Working on my Hulk Hogan look.  Thanks Harold.
Don't be so hasty...I bet there is all kinds of ice at those ponds I told you about...pike to be had there.
Well let me tell ya. FISHED OUT. The larger one has also been over run with seadoos. How they get them in is beyond me.
